Package com.heyho.demo.vendingmachine

Class ItemRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.heyho.demo.vendingmachine.ItemRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<ItemRow>

    public class ItemRow
extends Object
implements Comparable<ItemRow>
    A ItemRow represents a group of the same Item with of a certain size along with what label to file it under. You cannot store Items of different types under he same label. The only method of interest is vendItem() which is called to actually dispense an item from some row.
